title: Bumblebee Natural Foods
description: Opened in 1980, this vegetarian and organic store now has three shops clustered at the end of Brecknock Road (near Third Estate). The bakery sells freshly made hot and cold vegetarian food to take away with several vegan options such as samosas, pies, pizza, soup, salads and cakes. There's also an organic fruit and veg shop and a dry goods shop.
